data.description:
Looking for excitement? Craving entertainment? Take a break from reality and enter a new dimension of fun in the Ultimate Indoor Glow-in-the-Dark Mini Golf Experience at Putting Edge.  Whether eight or eighty, male or female, Putting Edge delivers a high energy, high quality experience that is ideal for an outing with family or friends, groups, corporate functions, birthday parties, and more, the possibilities are endless. 

Think Putting Edge for your next event! From a simple night out, to fundraisers, we make the event planning and execution process easy and hassle free.  Enjoy a fun one of a kind experience when you host a glow-in-the-dark event at Putting Edge! Whether you have a group of 10 or 100, throw an event that is sure to be enjoyed by all!

For further information, visit us online at www.PuttingEdge.com
